.Dd June 15, 2026
.Dt LIBVMDK 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm libvmdk.h
.Nd Library to access the VMware Virtual Disk (VMDK) format
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In libvmdk.h
.Pp
